    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>German goblets, usually made with a cover and often made of glass or silver, usually intended for presentation or other ceremonial purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
